 1993-18701993-09-240,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  CAN PORTS,  TB,  TC, 
PrecisAuthority for the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION to carry out a real estate transaction whereby it will acquire title from the Crown to one piece of land containing an area of some 746 m² and sell it to the Corporation of the District of North Vancouver IN EXCHANGE for the title to three irregularly-shaped pieces of land having a total combined area of 746 m², all the lands in question being situated near the Second Narrows Bridge, in the City of North Vancouver, British Columbia.
Attachments
precis:
Authority for the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION to carry out a real estate
transaction whereby it will acquire title from the Crown to one piece of
land containing an area of some 746 m² and sell it to the Corporation of
the District of North Vancouver IN EXCHANGE for the title to three
irregularly-shaped pieces of land having a total combined area of 746 m²,
all the lands in question being situated near the Second Narrows Bridge,
in the City of North Vancouver, British Columbia.
